      "content": "but what about the alternative though? if a government ignores things like education or healthcare just to pay down debt, doesnt that actually hurt stability in the long run because the people are struggling? seems like a bit of a catch-22. wouldn't investing in people actually help the economy grow and eventually fix the debt anyway?",
